ntentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":149,"content":"| ✅ | V2-T3-1 | **角色落盘**：正式五人写入 `data/characters/*.json`（agentId 与 personalityCode 对齐 docs/AI）；可与 golden 样例并存 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":150,"content":"| ✅ | V2-T3-2 | **第一幕真包**：新建 `data/storis-packages/wrong_number_act1/`（story.conf + 三张 s-card + canvas.layout）；叙事对齐 docs/AI 拓扑蓝本；packageId 禁用内存条旧名 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":163,"content":"- 任务 `verify` / `verify_default` exit 0","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":164,"content":"- Reviewer：`{workflow_dir}/reviews/latest.json` 中本轮 `blocker=0` 且 `critical=0`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":165,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":166,"content":"额外关注：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]}],"totalLines":24,"totalMatchedLines":5,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_6a691154-e4e1-45d6-aa89-90e04043e81","startedAtMs":"1784710259565","completedAtMs":"1784710259776"},"model_call_id":"0d884739-f63b-49e6-91e6-8851e24bc314-1-q3t3","session_id":"23a58b23-5fd0-4892-9832-41b782fa5f42","timestamp_ms":1784710259674}
